Platform Co-op Showcase 12 - FairBnB

"(9 mins) Sito Veracruz -- Veracruz’s is trying to create an alternative to Airbnb: Fairbnb. He proposes a short-stay rental platform that is beneficial to the city – with hosts who are registered with the council, and neighbors who are involved in the management of the platform. “I am talking about a platform that really complies with the principles of a fair, non-extractive and collaborative economy,” Veracruz said to the Guardian. “We would like to encourage visitors to stay in areas where they are not a disturbance, but could add something to the neighborhood.”



